(124641, 0, 0, 'Da princess wanna hear our reports straight away. Best not keep her waiting.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 98437, 133344, 'Shadow Hunter Mutumba to Player'),
(125122, 0, 0, 'Someting fell out of da sky! It be over here!', 14, 0, 100, 22, 0, 0, 133951, 'Darkspear Scout to Player'),
(125203, 0, 0, 'Blood and honor! Next time I see you, the drinks are on me!', 12, 0, 100, 4, 0, 0, 134010, 'Defiant Sailor'),
(125203, 1, 0, 'I owe you an ale!', 12, 0, 100, 4, 0, 98685, 0, 'Defiant Sailor'), -- BroadcastTextID: 61288 - 134013
(125245, 0, 0, 'Hey, uh... you\'ve been great and all, but we can handle the rest here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 101333, 134068, 'Newt to Player'),
(125245, 1, 0, 'You can ride my rocket back to your base. It\'s a one-way trip, though, so don\'t fire it up until you\'re all set to go.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 101334, 134069, 'Newt to Player'),
(125328, 0, 0, 'You! You have ruined everything... the frogs were meant to feed our magic for years!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134595, 'Priestess Zaldraxia to Player'),
(125328, 1, 0, 'Impudent SCUM! Our people will finally have our magic sated. No more thirsts! No more yearning!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134597, 'Priestess Zaldraxia'),
(125328, 2, 0, 'All your precious frogs will be caged. They will live to serve our needs!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134598, 'Priestess Zaldraxia'),
(125328, 3, 0, 'I will not fail you, Queen Azshara! The frogs shall be ours; I shall see to it!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134599, 'Priestess Zaldraxia'),
(125328, 4, 0, 'Why... we were so close... to never thirsting for magic... again...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134596, 'Priestess Zaldraxia to Player'),
(125392, 0, 0, 'My life... for... Azshara...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 98675, 144698, 'Vilescale Mana Taster to Player'),
(125393, 0, 0, 'We won\'t kill the frogs, but we\'ll slaughter you!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 134678, 'Vilescale Guardian to Player'),
(126039, 0, 0, '%s dies from his injuries.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mag\'ash the Poisonous to Player'), -- BroadcastTextID: 29303 - 29344 - 29356 - 29366 - 29392 - 29402 - 29412 - 49378 - 49389 - 135861
